Name: Attack Boost
Description: Increases attack power.
Description 2: Attack +5
Description 4:
Attack +2%
Bonus: +8

Name: Resentment
Description:
Increases attack when you have
recoverable damage (the red
portion of your Health Gauge).
Description 2: Attack +10 while active.
Description 4: Attack +20 while active.

Name: Adrenaline Rush
Description:
Temporarily increases attack power
after executing a perfectly-timed
evade just as a monster attacks.
Description 2: Attack +15 while active.
Description 4: Attack +25 while active.

Name: Offensive Guard
Description:
Temporarily increases attack
power after executing
a perfectly-timed guard.
Description 2: Attack +10% while active.

Name: Peak Performance
Description:
Increases attack when
your health is full.
Description 2: Attack +6 while active.
Description 4: Attack +15 while active.

Name: Counterstrike
Description:
Temporarily increases attack power after
being knocked back.
Description 2:
Attack +15 while active.
Moderately extends effect time.
Description 3:
Attack +25 while active.
Extends effect time.

Name: Critical Eye
Description: Increases affinity.
Description 2: Affinity +8%
Description 4: Affinity +16%

Name: Critical Boost
Description:
Increases the damage of
critical hits.
Description 1:
Increases damage dealt
by critical hits to 28%.
Description 2:
Increases damage dealt
by critical hits to 31%.
Description 3:
Increases damage dealt
by critical hits to 34%.
Description 4:
Increases damage dealt
by critical hits to 37%.
Description 5:
Increases damage dealt
by critical hits to 40%.

Name: Weakness Exploit
Description:
Increases the affinity of attacks
that exploit a monster's weak 
points and wounds.
Description 1:
Attacks that hit weak points gain
affinity +5%, with an extra 3%
on wounds.
Description 2:
Attacks that hit weak points gain
affinity +10%, with an extra 5%
on wounds.
Description 3:
Attacks that hit weak points gain
affinity +15%, with an extra 10%
on wounds.
Description 4:
Attacks that hit weak points have
20% increased affinity, with an
extra 15% on wounds.
Description 5:
Attacks that hit weak points have
30% increased affinity, with an
extra 20% on wounds.

Name: Critical Draw
Description:
Increases affinity when
performing draw attacks.
(Not effective while riding.)
Description 2: Affinity +75%

Name: Maximum Might
Description:
Increases affinity if stamina
is kept full for a period of time.
Description 2: Affinity +20% while active

Name: Fire Attack
Description:
Increases fire element attack
power. (Elemental attack power
has a maximum limit.)
Description 2:
Fire attack +10%
Bonus: +50

Name: Water Attack
Description:
Increases water element attack
power. (Elemental attack power
has a maximum limit.)
Description 2:
Water attack +10%
Bonus: +50

Name: Ice Attack
Description:
Increases ice element attack
power. (Elemental attack power
has a maximum limit.)
Description 2:
Ice attack +10%
Bonus: +50

Name: Thunder Attack
Description:
Increases thunder element attack
power. (Elemental attack power
has a maximum limit.)
Description 2:
Thunder attack +10%
Bonus: +50

Name: Dragon Attack
Description:
Increases dragon element attack
power. (Elemental attack power
has a maximum limit.)
Description 2:
Dragon attack +10%
Bonus: +50

Name: Poison Attack
Description:
Increases the rate of poison buildup.
(Poison buildup has a maximum limit.)
Description 2:
Poison buildup +10%
Bonus: +20

Name: Paralysis Attack
Description:
Increases the rate of paralysis buildup.
(Paralysis buildup has a maximum limit.)
Description 2:
Paralysis buildup +10%
Bonus: +20

Name: Sleep Attack
Description:
Increases the rate of sleep buildup.
(Sleep buildup has a maximum limit.)
Description 2:
Sleep buildup +10%
Bonus: +20

Name: Blast Attack
Description:
Increases the rate of blast buildup.
(Blast buildup has a maximum limit.)
Description 2:
Blast buildup +10%
Bonus: +20

Name: Critical Element
Description:
Increases elemental damage
(fire, water, thunder, ice, dragon)
when landing critical hits.
Description 1:
Slightly increases elemental damage
while active.
Description 2:
Increases elemental damage
while active.
Description 3:
Greatly increases elemental damage
while active.

Name: Critical Status
Description:
Increases abnormal status effects
(paralysis, poison, sleep, blast)
when landing critical hits.
Description 1:
Slightly increases abnormal
status effects when landing
critical hits.
Description 2:
Increases abnormal status effects
when landing critical hits.
Description 3:
Greatly increases abnormal
status effects when landing
critical hits.

Name: Charge Master
Description:
Increases element power and status
buildup for charged attacks.
Description 1:
Slightly increases elemental
damage and status buildup
for charged attacks.
Description 2:
Increases elemental damage
and status buildup for
charged attacks.
Description 3:
Greatly increases elemental
damage and status buildup
for charged attacks.

Name: Convert Element
Description:
After taking elemental damage,
temporarily grants you dragon element
effects. (Cooldown after effect ends.)
Description 1:
While active, deals extra dragon damage
after dealing enough elemental damage.
Slightly increases dragon attack.
Description 2:
Increases additional dragon damage
and increases dragon attack.
Description 3:
Further increases additional dragon
damage and greatly increases dragon
attack.

Name: Handicraft
Description:
Extends the weapon sharpness gauge.
However, it will not increase the
gauge past its maximum.
Description 2: Weapon sharpness +20
Description 4: Weapon sharpness +40

Name: Razor Sharp
Description:
Prevents your weapon from
losing sharpness.
Description 1:
Grants a 10% chance of no
sharpness loss.
Description 2:
Grants a 25% chance of no
sharpness loss.
Description 3:
Grants a 50% chance of no
sharpness loss.

Name: Protective Polish
Description:
Weapon sharpness does not decrease
for a set time after sharpening.
Description 1:
Grants no sharpness loss for
30 seconds after activation.
Description 2:
Grants no sharpness loss for
60 seconds after activation.
Description 3:
Grants no sharpness loss for
90 seconds after activation.

Name: Mind's Eye
Description:
Your attacks are deflected less and
deal more damage to hard targets.
Description 1:
50% chance of your attacks
not being deflected, +10%
damage to hard targets.
Description 2:
100% chance of your attacks
not being deflected, +15%
damage to hard targets.
Description 3:
100% chance of your attacks
not being deflected, +30%
damage to hard targets.

Name: Bludgeoner
Description:
Increases attack power when your
weapon sharpness is low.
Description 1:
+5% attack power when
your sharpness gauge is
yellow or lower.
Description 2:
+10% attack power when
your sharpness gauge is
yellow or lower.
Description 3:
+10% attack power when
your sharpness gauge is
green or lower.

Name: Master's Touch
Description:
Prevents your weapon from losing
sharpness during critical hits.
Description 1:
Grants an 80% chance of no
sharpness loss while active.

Name: Normal Shots
Description:
Increases the attack power of Normal
Ammo, normal arrows, and Flying
Swallow Shot.
Description 1:
Slightly increases the power of
specified ammo and arrows.

Name: Piercing Shots
Description:
Increases the attack of the bowgun's
Pierce Ammo, and the bow's Dragon
Piercer and Thousand Dragons.
Description 1:
Slightly increases the power of
specified ammo and arrows.

Name: Spread/Power Shots
Description:
Increases the attack of the bowgun's
Spread Ammo and the bow's Power
Shots and Quick Shots.
Description 1:
Slightly increases the power of
specified ammo and arrows.

Name: Ballistics
Description:
Extends the range in which ammo
and arrows have maximum power.
Description 2: Extends range.

Name: Rapid Fire Up
Description: Improves light bowgun rapid fire.

Name: Opening Shot
Description:
Increases the bowgun's reload speed
and increases the power of bullets
when fully loaded.
Description 1:
Moderately increases bowgun reload
speed and attack power of ammo
when certain conditions are met.
Description 2:
Increases bowgun reload speed
and attack power of ammo when
certain conditions are met.
Description 3:
Greatly increases bowgun reload
speed and attack power of ammo
when certain conditions are met.

Name: Tetrad Shot
Description:
Increases affinity of bowgun ammo/
coatings from the fourth shot and
attack of the fourth and sixth shots.
Description 1:
Slightly increases the attack
power and affinity of ammo
after certain conditions are met.
Description 2:
Moderately increases attack power
and affinity of ammo after certain
conditions are met.
Description 3:
Increases the attack power
and affinity of ammo after
certain conditions are met.

Name: Special Ammo Boost
Description:
Increases the power of the bowgun's
special ammo, and the bow's Dragon
Piercer, Thousand Dragons, and Tracer.
Description 1:
Moderately increases the power
of specified ammo and arrows.
Description 2:
Increases the power of specified
ammo and arrows.

Name: Poison Functionality
Description: Allows you to apply poison coatings.

Name: Para Functionality
Description: Allows you to apply paralysis coatings.

Name: Sleep Functionality
Description: Allows you to apply sleep coatings.

Name: Blast Functionality
Description: Allows you to apply blast coatings.

Name: Exhaust Functionality
Description: Allows you to apply exhaust coatings.

Name: Defense Boost
Description:
Increases defense. Also improves
resistances at higher levels.
Description 2: Defense +10
Description 4:
Defense +5%
Bonus: +20
All elemental resistances +3

Name: Divine Blessing
Description:
Has a predetermined chance of
reducing the damage you take.
Description 1:
While active, reduces damage
taken by 15%.
Description 2:
While active, reduces damage
taken by 30%.
Description 3:
While active, reduces damage
taken by 50%.

Name: Fire Resistance
Description:
Increases fire resistance.
Also improves defense at
higher levels.
Description 2: Fire resistance +12

Name: Water Resistance
Description:
Increases water resistance.
Also improves defense at
higher levels.
Description 2: Water resistance +12

Name: Thunder Resistance
Description:
Increases thunder resistance.
Also improves defense at
higher levels.
Description 2: Thunder resistance +12

Name: Ice Resistance
Description:
Increases ice resistance.
Also improves defense at
higher levels.
Description 2: Ice resistance +12

Name: Dragon Resistance
Description:
Increases dragon resistance.
Also improves defense at
higher levels.
Description 2: Dragon resistance +12

Name: Poison Resistance
Description: Reduces damage while poisoned.
Description 1:
Reduces the number of times
you take poison damage.
Description 2:
Greatly reduces the number of
times you take poison damage.

Name: Paralysis Resistance
Description: Reduces the duration of paralysis.
Description 1:
Reduces the duration
of paralysis by 30%.
Description 2:
Reduces the duration
of paralysis by 60%.

Name: Sleep Resistance
Description: Reduces the duration of sleep.
Description 1:
Reduces the duration
of sleep by 30%.
Description 2:
Reduces the duration
of sleep by 60%.

Name: Iron Skin
Description: Grants protection against defense down.
Description 1:
Reduces the duration of defense
down by 50%.
Description 2:
Reduces the duration of defense
down by 75%.

Name: Blight Resistance
Description:
Grants protection against all elemental
blights.
Description 1:
Reduces the duration of all
elemental blights by 50%.
Description 2:
Reduces the duration of all
elemental blights by 75%.

Name: Stun Resistance
Description: Reduces the duration of stun.
Description 1:
Reduces the duration
of stun by 30%.
Description 2:
Reduces the duration
of stun by 60%.

Name: Bleeding Resistance
Description: Grants protection against bleeding.
Description 2:
Greatly reduces damage while
bleeding.

Name: Bind Resistance
Description:
Grants protection against webbed
status and frostblight.
Description 1:
Allows you to quickly recover from
webbed status or frostblight.
Description 2:
Allows you to very quickly recover
from webbed status or frostblight.

Name: Blast Resistance
Description: Grants protection against blastblight.
Description 1:
Delays blastblight and reduces
blast damage.
Description 2:
Greatly delays blastblight and
greatly reduces blast damage.

Name: Stench Resistance
Description: Grants protection against stench.
Description 2: Prevents stench.

Name: Adaptability
Description:
Grants protection against environmental
damage, such as from heat or cold.
Description 1: Negates the effects of heat and cold.
Description 2: Negates environmental damage.

Name: Recovery Up
Description:
Increases the amount recovered
when restoring health.
Description 2: Moderately increases recovery.

Name: Recovery Speed
Description:
Speeds healing of recoverable
damage (the red portion of the
Health Gauge).
Description 1:
Doubles the speed at which
you heal recoverable damage.
Description 2:
Triples the speed at which
you heal recoverable damage.
Description 3:
Quadruples the speed at
which you heal recoverable
damage.

Name: Survival Expert
Description:
Extra health is recovered from
environmental interactables.
Description 2: Restores 80 health.

Name: Constitution
Description:
Reduces stamina depletion
when evading, blocking, or
doing certain other actions.
Description 2:
Reduces fixed stamina
depletion by 20%.
Description 4:
Reduces fixed stamina
depletion by 40%.

Name: Stamina Surge
Description: Speeds up stamina recovery.
Description 2: Stamina recovery speed +30%

Name: Marathon Runner
Description:
Slows down stamina depletion
for actions that continuously
drain stamina (such as dashing).
Description 2:
Reduces continuous stamina
depletion by 30%.

Name: Hunger Resistance
Description:
Reduces maximum stamina
depletion over time.
Description 1:
Extends the time until your
stamina cap reduces by 50%.
Description 2:
Extends the time until your
stamina cap reduces by 100%.
Description 3:
Prevents your stamina cap
from decreasing.

Name: Agitator
Description:
Increases attack power and
affinity when large monsters
become enraged.
Description 2:
Attack +8 and affinity +5%
while active.
Description 4:
Attack +16 and affinity +10%
while active.

Name: Latent Power
Description:
Temporarily increases affinity and
reduces stamina depletion when
certain conditions are met.
Description 1:
While active, affinity +10%
and reduces stamina
depletion by 30%.
Description 2:
While active, affinity +20%
and reduces stamina
depletion by 30%.
Description 3:
While active, affinity +30%
and reduces stamina
depletion by 50%.
Description 4:
While active, affinity +40%
and reduces stamina
depletion by 50%.
Description 5:
While active, affinity +50%
and reduces stamina
depletion by 50%.

Name: Heroics
Description:
Increases attack power and defense
when health drops to 35% or lower.
Description 2:
Attack +5% and defense +50
while active.
Description 4:
Attack +10% and defense +100
while active.
Description 5:
Attack +30% and defense-increasing
effects are negated while active.

Name: Burst
Description:
Continuously landing hits gradually
increases attack and elemental attack.
(Amount increased depends on weapon.)
Description 1:
On first hit, gain a small temporary
attack and element boost, replaced
by a larger boost after the fifth hit.
Description 2:
Hit 5 successive times for
a moderate stat boost.
Description 3:
Hit 5 successive times for
a bigger stat boost.
Description 4:
Hit 5 successive times for
an even bigger stat boost.
Description 5:
Hit 5 successive times for
a huge stat boost.

Name: Foray
Description:
Increases attack power and affinity
against large monsters affected by
poison or paralysis.
Description 1:
Attack +6 against large monsters
affected by poison or paralysis.
Description 2:
Attack +8 and affinity +5%
against large monsters affected
by poison or paralysis.
Description 3:
Attack +10 and affinity +10%
against large monsters affected
by poison or paralysis.
Description 4:
Attack +12 and affinity +15%
against large monsters affected
by poison or paralysis.
Description 5:
Attack +15 and affinity +20%
against large monsters affected
by poison or paralysis.

Name: Flayer
Description:
Makes it easier to inflict wounds. Upon
inflicting enough damage, also deals
additional non-elemental damage.
Description 1:
Makes it ever so slightly easier
to inflict wounds. Also deals
additional non-elemental damage.
Description 2:
Makes it moderately easier to inflict
wounds. Also deals slightly more
additional non-elemental damage.
Description 3:
Makes it easier to inflict wounds.
Also deals moderately more
additional non-elemental damage.
Description 4:
Makes it much easier to inflict
wounds. Also deals more additional
non-elemental damage.
Description 5:
Makes it significantly easier to
inflict wounds. Also deals much more
additional non-elemental damage.

Name: Palico Rally
Description: Powers up Palicoes.
Description 1:
Increases Palico attack power
and defense by 5%.
Description 2:
Increases Palico attack power
and defense by 10%.
Description 3:
Increases Palico attack power
and defense by 15%.
Description 4:
Increases Palico attack power
and defense by 20%.
Description 5:
Increases Palico attack power
and defense by 25%.

Name: Focus
Description:
Increases the fill rate for weapons
with gauges and the charge rate
for weapons with charge attacks.
Description 1:
Slightly increases gauge fill rate and
reduces charge times by 5%.
Description 2:
Moderately increases gauge fill rate
and reduces charge times by 10%.
Description 3:
Increases gauge fill rate and
reduces charge times by 15%.

Name: Power Prolonger
Description:
Allows long swords, dual blades, insect
glaives, switch axes, and charge blades
to stay powered up longer.
Description 1:
Moderately boosts the duration
weapons are powered up.
Description 2:
Boosts the duration weapons
are powered up.
Description 3:
Greatly boosts the duration
weapons are powered up.

Name: Punishing Draw
Description:
Adds a stun effect to draw attacks
and slightly increases attack power.
(Not effective while riding.)
Description 1:
Draw attacks deal a small
amount of stun damage
and gain attack +3.
Description 2:
Draw attacks deal a medium
amount of stun damage
and gain attack +5.
Description 3:
Draw attacks deal a large
amount of stun damage
and gain attack +7.

Name: Slugger
Description: Makes it easier to stun monsters.
Description 2: Stun power +30%

Name: Stamina Thief
Description:
Increases certain attacks'
ability to exhaust monsters.
Description 2: Exhaust power +30%

Name: Artillery
Description:
Strengthens explosive attacks like
shells, Wyvern's Fire, charge blade
phial attacks, and Sticky Ammo.
Description 1:
Moderately increases each attack
and Wyvern's Fire firing speed.
Shelling fire attack +30.
Description 2:
Increases each attack and
Wyvern's Fire firing speed.
Shelling fire attack +60.
Description 3:
Greatly increases each attack
and Wyvern's Fire firing speed.
Shelling fire attack +90.

Name: Rapid Morph
Description:
Increases switch speed and power
for switch axes and charge blades.
Description 2:
Speed +20%
Morph attack damage +10%

Name: Partbreaker
Description:
Makes it easier to break large monster
parts, and increases damage dealt when
destroying a wound with a Focus Strike.
Description 1:
Increases part damage and
damage dealt when conditions
are met by 10%.
Description 2:
Increases part damage and
damage dealt when conditions
are met by 20%.
Description 3:
Increases part damage and
damage dealt when conditions
are met by 30%.

Name: Coalescence
Description:
Temporarily increases elemental attack
power and status effects after recovering
from blights or abnormal status.
Description 1:
When active, grants a slight
increase to elemental damage
and status buildup.
Description 2:
When active, grants an
increase to elemental damage
and status buildup.
Description 3:
When active, grants a large
increase to elemental damage
and status buildup.

Name: Ambush
Description:
Temporarily increases damage
to large monsters with a successful
Sneak Attack.
Description 2: Attack +10% while active.

Name: Antivirus
Description:
Once infected, makes it easier
to overcome the Frenzy and
increases affinity if cured.
Description 1:
Slightly increases recovery rate
after contracting the Frenzy.
Affinity +3% if cured.
Description 2:
Increases recovery rate after
contracting the Frenzy.
Affinity +6% if cured.
Description 3:
Greatly increases recovery rate
after contracting the Frenzy.
Affinity +15% if cured.

Name: Elemental Absorption
Description:
After taking elemental damage,
temporarily grants you element
effects. (Cooldown after effect ends)
Description 1:
While active, slightly increases
elemental attack, and resistance
to element taken at activation by 4.
Description 2:
While active, moderately increases
elemental attack, and resistance
to element taken at activation by 6.
Description 3:
While active, increases elemental
attack, and resistance to element
taken at activation by 8.

Name: Horn Maestro
Description:
Increases the effect duration of
hunting horn melodies. (Effect lost
when you change weapons.)
Description 1:
Extends Melody Effect duration
and increases the chance of larger
heals from healing melodies.
Description 2:
Greatly increases the effect
duration of hunting horn
melodies.

Name: Charge Up
Description:
Increases your power to induce
stun when you hit a monster with
a hammer's charged attack.

Name: Airborne
Description:
Increases the damage caused by jumping
attacks.

Name: Self-Improvement
Description:
Attack and defense increase as time
passes while on a quest. (The maximum
is reached after 30 minutes.)

Name: Poison Duration Up
Description:
Extends the duration of your poison's
effect on monsters.
Description 1:
Extends the duration of your
poison's effect by 20%.

Name: Guard
Description:
Reduces knockbacks and stamina
depletion when guarding.
Description 1:
Slightly decreases the impact
of attacks and reduces stamina
depletion by 15%.
Description 2:
Decreases the impact of attacks and
reduces stamina depletion by 30%.
Description 3:
Greatly decreases the impact of
attacks and reduces stamina
depletion by 50%.

Name: Evade Window
Description:
Extends the invulnerability period
when evading.
Description 2:
Slightly increases
invulnerability window.
Description 4:
Greatly increases
invulnerability window.

Name: Evade Extender
Description: Increases evade distance.
Description 2: Extends evasion distance.

Name: Earplugs
Description:
Grants protection from large monsters'
roars.
Description 1:
Reduces the effects of weak
monster roars.
Description 2:
Nullifies weak monster roars and
reduces the effects of strong
monster roars.
Description 3:
Nullifies weak and strong
monster roars.

Name: Guard Up
Description:
Allows you to guard against
ordinarily unblockable attacks.
Description 2: Reduces damage taken by 50%.

Name: Quick Sheathe
Description: Speeds up weapon sheathing.
Description 2: Increases sheathing speed.

Name: Windproof
Description: Grants protection against wind pressure.
Description 1:
Negates minor wind pressure
and halves the effects of
major wind pressure.
Description 2:
Negates minor and major wind
pressure and halves the effects
of dragon wind pressure.
Description 3: Negates all kinds of wind pressure.

Name: Tremor Resistance
Description:
Grants protection against ground
tremors.
Description 1:
Nullifies very minor ground tremors
and halves effects of minor ground
tremors.
Description 2:
Nullifies up to minor ground tremors
and greatly reduces the effects of
major ground tremors.

Name: Flinch Free
Description:
Prevents knockbacks and other reactions
to small damage.
Description 2:
Prevents knockbacks. Tripping is
reduced to a knockback instead.

Name: Intimidator
Description:
Reduces the chance small monsters
will attack after spotting you.
(Has no effect on certain monsters.)
Description 1:
Discourages monsters from engaging
you even if you've been spotted.
Description 2:
Highly discourages monsters from
engaging you even if you've
been spotted.
Description 3:
Prevents monsters from engaging
you even if you've been spotted.

Name: Speed Eating
Description:
Increases meat-eating and
item-consumption speed.
Description 2: Increases eating speed.

Name: Load Shells
Description:
Improves reloading, and increases
the gunlance's shell capacity and
charge blade's phial capacity.
Description 1:
Increases shell and phial
reloading speed.
Description 2:
Increases shell/phial reloading speed.
Gunlance loading capacity +1. Charge
blade charges 5 phials on yellow gauge.

Name: Aquatic/Oilsilt Mobility
Description:
Grants resistance against
impairments to mobility while
in water, oilsilt, or streams.
Description 1:
Negates the effects of muddy streams,
and prevents you from being slowed
down in water or oilsilt.
Description 2: Also negates the effects of waves.

Name: Shock Absorber
Description:
Disables damage reactions when you
hit a friend or when a friend hits you.

Name: Leap of Faith
Description:
Allows you to do a dive-evade when
facing towards large monsters and
extends the dive-evade distance.

Name: Jump Master
Description:
Prevents attacks from knocking
you back during a jump.

Name: Cliffhanger
Description:
Decreases stamina depletion
when climbing on vines.
Description 1:
Reduces stamina depletion while
climbing by 50%.

Name: Wide-Range
Description:
Allows the effects of certain
items to also affect nearby allies.
Description 1:
Items affect nearby allies
with 33% of their efficacy.
Description 2:
Items affect nearby allies
in a wider radius with 33%
of their efficacy.
Description 3:
Items affect nearby allies
in a wider radius with 66%
of their efficacy.
Description 4:
Items affect nearby allies
in a much wider radius with
66% of their efficacy.
Description 5:
Items affect nearby allies
in a much wider radius with
full efficacy.

Name: Tool Specialist
Description:
Reduces the recharge time for
specialized tools.
Description 2: Shortens recharge time by 20%.
Description 4: Shortens recharge time by 40%.

Name: Bombardier
Description:
Increases the damage
of explosive items.
Description 2: Explosive power +20%

Name: Mushroomancer
Description:
Lets you digest mushrooms that
would otherwise be inedible and
gain their advantageous effects.
Description 1:
Lets you digest blue mushrooms
and toadstools.
Description 2:
Additionally lets you digest
nitroshrooms and parashrooms.
Description 3:
Additionally lets you digest
mandragoras, devil's blight,
and exciteshrooms.

Name: Item Prolonger
Description:
Extends the duration
of some item effects.
Description 2: Item effect duration +25%

Name: Free Meal
Description:
Gives you a predetermined
chance of consuming a food
or drink item for free.
Description 2: Activates 25% of the time.

Name: Speed Sharpening
Description:
Speeds up weapon sharpening
when using a whetstone.
Description 1:
Removes one cycle from
the sharpening process.
Description 2:
Removes two cycles from
the sharpening process.

Name: Blindsider
Description:
Improves the effectiveness of flash
attacks and items.
Description 1:
Improves the effectiveness of
flash attacks and items.

Name: Botanist
Description:
Increases the quantity of herbs and
other consumable items you gather.
Description 1:
One extra consumable herb
item per gather.
Description 2:
Additionally adds one extra
consumable fruit, nut, or seed
item per gather.
Description 3:
Additionally adds one extra
consumable insect item per
gather.
Description 4:
Additionally adds one extra
consumable mushroom item
per gather.

Name: Geologist
Description:
Increases the number of items you gain
at gathering points.
Description 1:
One extra item when gathering
from bonepiles.
Description 2:
Additionally adds one extra item
when gathering special items.
Description 3:
Additionally adds one extra item
when gathering from mining
outcrops.

Name: Entomologist
Description:
The bodies of small insect monsters
won't be destroyed, allowing them
to be carved.

Name: Outdoorsman
Description:
Improves fishing, grilling,
and transporting abilities.
Description 1:
Improves fishing, grilling,
and transporting abilities.

Name: Neopteron Alert
Description 3:
Increases the amount of honey
you gain from gathering points.

Name: Neopteron Camouflage
Description 3:
Increases movement speed while
crouching, and makes it easier to
escape large monsters' detection.

Name: Scaling Prowess
Description 3:
Makes it easier to mount monsters
and to wound them once mounted.

Name: Scale Layering
Description 3:
Temporarily reduces stamina depletion

Name: Flexible Leathercraft
Description 3:
Increases gathering speed, and

or carving.

Name: Buttery Leathercraft

Increases your affinity temporarily

Name: Fortifying Pelt

Increases attack and defense after

Name: Alluring Pelt

Name: Lord's Favor

Temporarily increases attack power

Name: Lord's Fury
Description 3:
Increases attack when inflicted with
ailments.

Name: Guardian's Pulse
Description 3:
Increases recovery speed of stamina

Name: Guardian's Protection

Reduces elemental and unique damage

Name: Imparted Wisdom

Name: Doshaguma's Might
Description 2:
Temporarily grants attack +10

or Offset attack
Description 4:
Temporarily grants attack +25
after a successful Power Clash
or Offset attack

Name: Rathalos's Flare

Chance to deal additional fire
damage after landing an attack.
Description 4:
Increases additional fire damage
after landing an attack.

Name: Xu Wu's Vigor
Description 2:
Temporarily grants attack +15 after
eating items such as well-done steak.
Description 4:
Temporarily grants attack +25 after
eating items such as well-done steak.

Name: Gravios's Protection

Reduces the damage you take by 5%

Description 4:
Reduces the damage you take by 10%
when your health is full.

Name: Blangonga's Spirit
Description 2:
Using the <BOLD>To Victory!</BOLD> gesture moderately 
increases attack temporarily to nearby allies.
Greatly effects Palicoes and Support Hunters.
Description 4:
Using the <BOLD>To Victory!</BOLD> gesture increases
attack temporarily to nearby allies. Greatly
effects Palicoes and Support Hunters.

Name: Ebony Odogaron's Power
Description 2:
Extends the duration of the Burst

Burst is active.
Description 4:
Further extends the duration of
the Burst skill and grants attack +10
while Burst is active.

Name: Fulgur Anjanath's Will
Description 2: Grants an additional Stamina Gauge.
Description 4: Grants an additional long Stamina Gauge.

Name: Uth Duna's Cover
Description 2:
Increases defense temporarily when
using a specialized tool.
Description 4:
Greatly increases defense and
resistance temporarily when
using a specialized tool.

Name: Rey Dau's Voltage
Description 2:
Moderately extends the activation

Description 4:
Extends the activation time of the
Latent Power skill.

Name: Nu Udra's Mutiny
Description 2:
Deals moderate additional damage

Description 4:
Deals additional damage while the
Resentment skill is active.

Name: Jin Dahaad's Revolt

Greatly increases attack after recovering
from webbed status, frostblight, being
pinned, or a Power Clash.

Name: Gore Magala's Tyranny
Description 2:
Infects you with Frenzy when against
large monsters.
Description 4:
Infects you with Frenzy and raises

Name: Arkveld's Hunger
Description 2:
Regenerates a small amount of your health

Regenerates your health as you continually
attack a monster. Recovery varies by
weapon.

Name: Guardian Arkveld's Vitality

Restores a moderate amount of health
when destroying a wound on a large
monster.

Restores health when destroying a wound

Name: Mizutsune's Prowess

Prevents major bubbleblight and

Prevents major bubbleblight and ups

Description 1:
Affinity +3% when wet, and +7%

Description 2:
Affinity +6% when wet, and +14%
while afflicted with bubbleblight.
Description 3:
Affinity +9% when wet, and +21%
while afflicted with bubbleblight.

Name: Zoh Shia's Pulse
Description 2:
Allows the Health Gauge to continue

Description 4:
Allows the Health Gauge to continue
to recover up to the max value,
even if there is no red portion.

Name: Whiteflame Torrent
Description:
Chance to deal additional damage
after landing an attack.
Description 1:
Activates skill effect. (When used
with Scorcher, does not stack but
adds extra fire damage.)

Name: Lord's Soul
Description 3:
Boosts attack and lowers defense
but lets you survive one lethal hit.
Afterwards, boosts defense and res.

Name: Blossomdance Prayer
Description 2:
During Blossomdance, adds
special items to quest rewards.
(No effect when joining mid-quest.)
Description 4:
During Blossomdance, adds special
items to quest rewards, and
greatly boosts attack and defense.

Name: Festival Spirit
Description 3:
Lets you carve one additional time
from carcasses during quests.
(No effect when joining mid-quest.)

Name: Glory's Favor
Description 3:
Increases quest target rewards.
(No effect when joining mid-quest.)

Name: Defender Meal (Lo)
Description: Sometimes decreases damage taken.

Name: Defender Meal (Hi)
Description: Often decreases damage taken.

Name: Black Belt Meal (Lo)
Description:
Reduces stamina depletion
when performing stamina-draining
moves such as evading, etc.

Name: Black Belt Meal (Hi)
Description:
Greatly reduces stamina depletion
when performing stamina-draining
moves such as evading, etc.

Name: Tumbler Meal (Lo)
Description:
Slightly extends the invulnerability
period when evading.

Name: Tumbler Meal (Hi)
Description:
Extends the invulnerability
period when evading.

Name: Moxie Meal (Lo)
Description:
Prevents fainting one time when

remaining health.

Name: Moxie Meal (Hi)
Description:
Prevents fainting one time and

exceeds your remaining health.

Name: Caprice Meal (Lo)
Description:
Repeatedly activates a temporary
attack boost at random intervals.

Name: Caprice Meal (Hi)
Description:
Repeatedly activates a large
temporary attack boost at
random intervals.

Description:
Lessens the effects of various
ailments.

Name: Medic Meal
Description:
Increases the amount of health

Name: Swimmer Meal
Description: Increases attack when wet.

Name: Specialist Meal

Increases the potency of
abnormal status attacks.

Name: Gatherer Meal
Description:
Sometimes increases the number
of resources per gather of bones,
ore, and other gatherable items.
